@startuml

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign direction
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
autonumber

actor Voter
entity VotingApplication as "Voting Application"
entity DigitalBallotBox as "Digital Ballot Box"
database PublicBulletinBoard as "Public Bulletin Board"

VotingApplication -> DigitalBallotBox: Ballot submission bulletin with ballot\nencrypted with fresh randomizers
DigitalBallotBox -> PublicBulletinBoard: Publish ballot submission bulletin
VotingApplication <-- DigitalBallotBox: Ballot submission bulletin tracker
Voter <-- VotingApplication: Present tracker hash for input\nto ballot check application,\nask whether to check or cast

@enduml
